divs: Sighting Details I go outside and smoke because we don't like the kids to smell it and at nite I look to the skies to see if there is any thing to see. I know what plains are and the space station look like when they have passed. This was differant. This object came out of know where's and passed across this fairly good size star and covered it. the lights is what made this object differant. They flashed differant colors not like plains do. And I mean flashed It had many colors. it didn't last long but it was beautiful to watch and by the time I asked my wife to come and look, it was gone. Amazing site to see!!
Summary: looking at stars then what looked like differant flashing lights like a camera flash passed accross this star at very high rate of speed then slowed down really fast than resomned it's face pace off into the trees.
